(461, 1, '2021-06-03 14:12:59', '2021-06-03 14:12:59', '<p>[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1622729630346{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\n<div class=\"vc_title_page\">\n<p><a href=\"#\">Trang ch </a> / Thng tin chung / Cu hi thng gp</p>\n<p class=\"vc_content_title\">Thng tin chung</p>\n</div>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"vc_sibar_thongtin\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1622730287256{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"]</p>\n<div class=\"vc_page_thongtin_tab\"><a href=\"/vcoating/thong-tin-chung/\">Tin tc &amp; s kin</a><a href=\"/vcoating/thong-tin-chung-co-hoi-nghe-nghep/\">C hi ngh nghip</a><a class=\"active\">Cu hi thng gp</a></div>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1622730868440{margin-top: 15px !important;margin-bottom: 29px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h1>Cu hi thng gp</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong> thun tin v tit kim thi gian cho Qu khch, di y chng ti xin c tng hp nhng cu hi ph bin nht t khch hng m chng ti nhn c:</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">1. a ch nh my V-COATING  u?</p>\n<p>Nh my V-COATING nm trong khun vin Khu Cng nghip Dt may Ph Ni B, x Liu X, huyn Yn M, tnh Hng Yn (giai on II  st nt giao QL5 v QL39A), l cng ty th 3 nm bn tay tri Qu khch hng khi i theo hng t cng KCN vo. Qu khch hng c th tham kho hng dn ch ng  trang ch.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">2. Lnh vc kinh doanh ca cng ty l g?</p>\n<p>Lnh vc kinh doanh chnh ca V-COATING l gia cng, thi cng, lp dng cc sn phm kt cu thp phc v cc d n vin thng, giao thng, in lc v dch v m km nhng nng. Cng sut xng m km: 80.000 tn/nm; Cng sut xng kt cu thp: 40.000 tn/nm.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">3. Kch thc b m ca nh my V-Coating l bao nhiu? Sn phm qu kh, phi tiu chun c m c khng? Hng ca chng ti cn lu  g trc khi mang hng n m?</p>\n<p>Kch thc b m ti nh my V-COATING l: 12,6m (Di) x 1,6m (Rng) x 2,6m (Cao)</p>\n<p>Nu Sn phm ca Qu khch hng vt qu kch thc b, Qu khch vui lng lin h trc tip vi chng ti  c t vn v phng n m. Cc im cn lu  trc khi mang hng ti m:</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch  c thit  m bo cng ngh thot m cha?</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch c vt qu kch thc b khng?</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch  loi b cc yu t ri ro v cong vnh cha?</p>\n<p> Qu khch mun m theo tiu chun no?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">4. Thi gian  m v hon thin sn phm l bao lu?</p>\n<p>Chu trnh m v hon thin sn phm ti cng ty ti t khi hng c a vo dy truyn sn xut n khi hon thin l khong 4h-6h lm vic ty thuc tnh cht hng ha v khi lng Qu khch hng c th lin h trc nu c pht sinh nhu cu c bit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">5. Hng sau m c c h tr ng kin khng? C dch v sn sau m khng?</p>\n<p>Hng sau m s c ng kin theo quy cch ca nh sn xut, nu Qu khch hng yu cu ng kin theo quy cch ring, vui lng lm vic  thng nht trc vi chng ti v n gi v cch thc thc hin.<br />\nTng t vi sn hay phun bi (lm sch b mt trc m) chng ti u c th p ng nu Qu khch hng c nhu cu. Vui lng lin h hotline: 090 8855 689 hoc gi email v a ch: info@vcoating.vn  bit thm thng tin chi tit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>6. Thi gian b phn kho/giao nhn hng ha ca nh my bt u v kt thc thi gian lm vic trong ngy?</p>\n<p>B phn kho lm vic nh sau: Bui sng t 7h30  11h30; bui chiu t 13h00  17h00. Tuy nhin nu c nhu cu pht sinh xut nhp ngoi khung gi ny, Qu khch hng c th bo trc vi nhn vin ph trch n hng ca V-COATING  c h tr.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id=\"blog-sidebar\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1622730854462{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h3>Tin khc</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1622731960373{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\"][vc_column][s7upf_posts item_style=\"style2\" column=\"3\" number=\"3\" cats=\"\" el_class=\"vc_post_tinkhac\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1622731177198{margin-top: 20px !important;border-top-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 28px !important;border-top-color: #d9d9d9 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Cu hi thng gp', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cau-hoi-thuong-gap', '', '', '2021-06-03 14:52:43', '2021-06-03 14:52:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/vcoating/?page_id=461', 0, 'page', '', 0),
