 v phng n m. Cc im cn lu  trc khi mang hng ti m:</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch  c thit  m bo cng ngh thot m cha?</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch c vt qu kch thc b khng?</p>\n<p> Sn phm ca Qu khch  loi b cc yu t ri ro v cong vnh cha?</p>\n<p> Qu khch mun m theo tiu chun no?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">4. Thi gian  m v hon thin sn phm l bao lu?</p>\n<p>Chu trnh m v hon thin sn phm ti cng ty ti t khi hng c a vo dy truyn sn xut n khi hon thin l khong 4h-6h lm vic ty thuc tnh cht hng ha v khi lng Qu khch hng c th lin h trc nu c pht sinh nhu cu c bit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"vc_cauhoi\">5. Hng sau m c c h tr ng kin khng? C dch v sn sau m khng?</p>\n<p>Hng sau m s c ng kin theo quy cch ca nh sn xut, nu Qu khch hng yu cu ng kin theo quy cch ring, vui lng lm vic  thng nht trc vi chng ti v n gi v cch thc thc hin.<br />\nTng t vi sn hay phun bi (lm sch b mt trc m) chng ti u c th p ng nu Qu khch hng c nhu cu. Vui lng lin h hotline: 090 8855 689 hoc gi email v a ch: info@vcoating.vn  bit thm thng tin chi tit.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>6. Thi gian b phn kho/giao nhn hng ha ca nh my bt u v kt thc thi gian lm vic trong ngy?</p>\n<p>B phn kho lm vic nh sau: Bui sng t 7h30  11h30; bui chiu t 13h00  17h00. Tuy nhin nu c nhu cu pht sinh xut nhp ngoi khung gi ny, Qu khch hng c th bo trc vi nhn vin ph trch n hng ca V-COATING  c h tr.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id=\"blog-sidebar\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1622730854462{margin-top: 20px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h3>Tin khc</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Cu hi thng gp', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '461-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-03 14:34:16', '2021-06-03 14:34:16', '', 461, 'http://localhost/vcoating/?p=470', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
